# Pre-signed transactions

The Union IBC stack uses the address `0xC33241a8A660d1089E3E5838b8eB39aE8090C077` to deploy the deployer at  `0x6Dd4E0224D46b60D86e57c9E5980589E9818020F`. This file contains pre-signed transactions that can be used on new chains.

All of the transactions have the gas limit set to `300000`. The gas price varies, and can be verified with the following command:

```sh
cast dt $TX | jq .gasPrice -r | cast to-dec
```

Which will return the amount in `wei`. This can then be converted to `gwei` with `cast`:

```sh
cast to-unit $GAS gwei
```

Known deployments can be found at [deployments/evm-deployer.json](../../deployments/evm-deployer.json).
